snippet.title: Jazz Jack Rabbit 2 Intro
snippet.description:
Jazz Jack Rabbit 2 Intro

This nonviolent but addictive game features a rabbit that can fire weapons and, on occasion, helicopter with his ears. As Jazz, your objective is to shoot blocks with stars on them and stomp on blocks that have exclamation marks. The game includes dynamic lighting, scaling, rotation, and warping. This version supports flaming and freezing weapons.
